The only way the drafting history of Pandas could be interpreted as rejecting creationism is if the authors had discarded not just the word, but the explanation of what the word means Ñ Òvarious forms of life began abruptly through an intelligent agency with their distinctive features already intact Ñ fish with fins and scales, birds with feathers, beaks, and wings, etc.Ó The retention of the central creationist concepts using a different term, Òintelligent design,Ó dictates only one inference: intelligent design equals creationism.
